message.body: I'm at work for a few more hours. I haven't heard back from Beth but I'll call her again late night / early tomorrow.
I just spoke with Cindy. Please call me when you get a chance.
Fuck. I meant Beth. I don't want to talk to Cindy ever again.
Lol
Just saw this text
Text me Beth's number again Srry will save this time
As I said she is a little intense but just amazing at killing bugs.
I sent you that email. Pls let me know if we need cleaning supplies. Thanks again!
I just spoke with Beth again. She said you called & spoke for awhile. She said she mentioned getting Tupperware. I'll be happy to reimburse your for any of that stuff.
Really?!!! That would be Awesome!!
Bc I'm broooooke haha
This space at the crane is a bit expensive to first set up!!
Eventually it'll be a small earning gig bc I make 30% of sales, but now it's a money pit :( had to buy drill /dry wall anchors/booklet/frame for artist statement/wall paint/key fob blegh
So many hidden start up costs that I was not expecting at all
Ok. I can order stuff online thru Target / Home Depot / Lowes etc & try to get someone to pick it up.
Anyway yeah I was like Oh yes plastic containers are smart
But I have no money for that lol
I can order! I'll text you screen grabs and you tell me if it's OK price range - I'll get cheap stuff
And you can keep it in basement when we are done
For future tenants
If you go online & send me what you need a can pay with my debit card.
In case they have bed bug issues and this needs to be done again, which I'm sure it will since it's so many people
Ok!!! Perfect!
Well I'm hoping Beth will get rid of these guys & we will wont have that issue for a long long time.
I got your email. How many containers should I order? 2? 3?
3 sounds good I think?
Sounds good. I'll see if Avery can pick them up.
Also I was thinking about what you said about the gallery. I don't want to offer for someone else but I bet Jonny Man probably could help you out.
